  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ja tad pee winna irr tas\nEngelis/ tas Aiſtahwetais/ tas\nveenajs no tuhkſtoſcheem/ Zil-\nvekan faru Taifnibu ſtahſtiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad buhs wiſch tam\nchehligs/ un fazzijis : Atpeſti to/\na tas eekſch Samaitaſchanas\nie nogruinſt/ es efmu Salihſi-\nnachanu atraddis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad buhs winna Meefa\naltaka ne ka Jauniba/ wiſch\nnahks atkaſ pee farwas Jaunibas\naika.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſch Deewu luhs/\nas winnu ſchehlohs/ un uſskat-\nihs winna Waiqu ar Preeku/\nin atdoſs tam Zilwekam farwu\nTaifnibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad wiſch iſteiks preeſſch\nZilwekeim/ un fazzijis : Es bijn\ngrehkojs/ un to Teeſu pahrgroh-\niis/ bet tas man ne irr par lab-\nu bijis/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "(Tomehr) Wiſch irr\nnannu Dwehfelt atpeſtis/ ka ta\neekſch Samaitaſchanas ne grün-\nn/ ta ka manna Dſihwiba to\nGatschumu reds.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Naugt / ſcho wiſtu pa-\narr tas STIPRAJS\nDEEWS diwi jeb trihſkahrt\nar Zilivekn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka tas winna Dwehfeli\nnowehrſch no tahs Samatta-\nchanas/ ka wiſch avgaisinohts\ntohp eekſch tahs Galſmas to\nDſihwu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Uſmanni Ijabs / klaufi\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Irr teiw Wallodas/ tad\natbildi man/ runna/ jo man irr\nlabs Prahts teiw taitſnoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ja newaid/ tad klaust\nman/ zeet kluffu/ es gribbu teiw\nGudribu mahziht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XXXIV. Nodalla.\nElijus runna wehl wairak/ un aprahi Ijabu/\nka wiſch fazzijis : Tam Deewabihiſgam\nſchai Paſaulē ta patt flahiohte ka tam Bes-\ndeewigam : 1. Jo Deews effu taiſns/ un\ntweens Eohgis tahs Paſuales/ tapehz wiſch\narri netaiſni nefohd : 10. Un jeſchir wiſch\ntam Besdeewigam Meeru dohdus/ tad ue\nweenſ winnam to ware leege : 29. Wehle/\nka Ijabs to grihbetu wehra life un pakla-\nſiht : 33. Ja ne/ ka Deews winnu weht\njo wairak fohtiſu un pahrmahziſu : 36.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Klaufajt juhs Gud-\nrt mannu Wallodu / un juhs\nSaprattiqi atgreeſeet tahs Au-\nfis pee mannim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ta Auſs pahrbanda\ntohs Wahrdus/ itt ka tas\nSchohds to Bartibu bauda.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Lat mehs fawa Starpd\nto Teeju neſaim/ lat mehs fawa\nStarpd atſibſtain/ kas labs irr-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo Ijabs irr fazzijis : Es\ncimu taiſns/ un tas STIP-\nRAJS DEEWS irr mannu\nTeeſu atſehmis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es tohpu par Meſkuli tur-\nrehts pee mannas Teeſas/ man-\nna * Mohziba irr breeſniga/ beſ\nwiſtas Pahrfahpfchanas.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
